videos.description: Troy Caupain pulls up and makes 3 to give Cincinnati and early 3-2 lead.
videos.headline: Caupain drains the 3-pointer to give Bearcats early lead

videos.description: Jarron Cumberland hits the open 3 from the wing to give Cincinnati a 23-12 lead.
videos.headline: Cumberland hits open 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Evans finishes break with the jam
